%% Activity Diagram: Adding a Dish to Basket
graph TD
    A[User logs in] -->|Is authentication successful?| B{Authentication successful?}
    B -- Yes --> C[View menu]
    C --> D[Select dish to add to cart]
    D --> E[Send request to API to add dish]
    E -->|Does dish exist?| F{Dish exists?}
    F -- Yes --> G[Add dish to user basket]
    G --> H[Return success message]
    F -- No --> I[Show error message]
    B -- No --> J[Show login error]
